程序包 org.group05.analyzer.dataStructure

类 CallRecord

java.lang.Object
org.group05.analyzer.dataStructure.CallRecord
public class CallRecord extends Object
This class is used to store the information of a call record. A call record is a record of a method call in the code. It contains the information of the callee method, the caller method and the arguments. It also contains a boolean list to store whether this call record is related to multi-layer calls.
